<bibRefCitation author="Viraktamath" box="[527,959,1251,1277]" lastPageId="8" lastPageNumber="25" pageId="8" pageNumber="24" refString="Viraktamath, C. A. and S. Viraktamath (1992) Revision of the deltocephaline leafhoppers of the grass-feeding genus Leofa Distant (Insecta, Homoptera, Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadellidae). Entomologische Abhandlungen, 55, 1 - 12. Zahniser, J. N. and C. H. Dietrich (2008) Phylogeny of the leafhopper subfamily Deltocephalinae (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadellidae) and related subfamilies based on morphology. Systematics and Biodiversity, 6, 1 - 24. Zahniser, J. N. and A. Hicks. (2007) Three new species of Icaia Linnavuori (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Deltocephalinae) from Peru and distinction of the genus from Athysanella Baker. Zootaxa, 1390, 27 - 29." type="journal article" year="1992">
